424// ========== FRIEND FUNCTION IMPLEMENTATIONS ========== //
425namespace OpenXLSX
426{
433 inline bool operator==(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
434 {
435 return XLRow::isEqual(lhs, rhs);
436 }
437
444 inline bool operator!=(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
445 {
446 return !(lhs.m_rowNode == rhs.m_rowNode);
447 }
448
455 inline bool operator<(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
456 {
457 return XLRow::isLessThan(lhs, rhs);
458 }
459
466 inline bool operator>(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
467 {
468 return (rhs < lhs);
469 }
470
477 inline bool operator<=(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
478 {
479 return !(lhs > rhs);
480 }
481
488 inline bool operator>=(const XLRow& lhs, const XLRow& rhs)
489 {
490 return !(lhs < rhs);
491 }
492
493} // namespace OpenXLSX
